name: |A message worth repeating|
description:
Bitcoin art displayed in
the infinity room, including the
Satoshi icon mask, Better Money
campbells soup can & red bull
labels, framed design elements
from the Creation and
Destruction piece, PR man, and
Satoshi's Citadel. Using a variety
of visual styles, the message is
consistent. Bitcoin is better
money. 1024 x 1080px. GIF
